tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE real_estate_plans (
  plan_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  plan_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  project_id INT NOT NULL,
  progress_percentage INT,
  timeline DATE,
  budget DECIMAL
)

CREATE TABLE DevelopmentPlans (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  project_name VARCHAR(255),
  progress DECIMAL(5,2),
  timeline DATE,
  budget DECIMAL(10,2)
);

CREATE TABLE Projects (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  plan_id INT,
  project_name VARCHAR(255),
  start_date DATE,
  end_date DATE,
  budget_allocated DECIMAL(10,2),
  budget_spent DECIMAL(10,2)
);

CREATE TABLE development_plans (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    project_name VARCHAR(255),
    progress INT,
    timeline DATE,
    budget DECIMAL(10,2)
);

CREATE TABLE projects (
    project_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    plan_id INT,
    status VARCHAR(50),
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE,
    budget_used DECIMAL(10,2)
);
CREATE TABLE RealEstateProjects ( project_id BIGINT PRIMARY KEY, project_name VARCHAR(255), start_date DATE, end_date DATE, budget DECIMAL(10,2) );
CREATE TABLE ProjectProgress ( progress_id BIGINT PRIMARY KEY, project_id BIGINT, progress_description TEXT, progress_date DATE, FOREIGN KEY (project_id) REFERENCES RealEstateProjects(project_id) );
CREATE TABLE ProjectTimelines ( timeline_id BIGINT PRIMARY KEY, project_id BIGINT, timeline_date DATE, timeline_description TEXT, FOREIGN KEY (project_id) REFERENCES RealEstateProjects(project_id) );
CREATE TABLE ProjectBudgeting ( budget_id BIGINT PRIMARY KEY, project_id BIGINT, budget_amount DECIMAL(10,2), budget_date DATE, FOREIGN KEY (project_id) REFERENCES RealEstateProjects(project_id) );

CREATE TABLE real_estate_projects (
  project_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  project_name VARCHAR(255),
  project_location VARCHAR(255),
  project_start_date DATE,
  project_end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE project_progress (
  progress_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  project_id INT,
  task_name VARCHAR(255),
  task_description TEXT,
  task_status VARCHAR(50),
  task_completion_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE project_timelines (
  timeline_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  project_id INT,
  milestone_name VARCHAR(255),
  milestone_description TEXT,
  milestone_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE project_budgets (
  budget_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  project_id INT,
  budget_category VARCHAR(255),
  budget_amount DECIMAL(10, 2),
  budget_spent DECIMAL(10, 2)
);

CREATE TABLE project_teams (
  team_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  project_id INT,
  team_name VARCHAR(255),
  team_lead VARCHAR(100),
  team_member_1 VARCHAR(100),
  team_member_2 VARCHAR(100)
);
